	<h1 class="title">除了显示屏，大猩猩玻璃还会用在哪？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/998/small/998.jpg?1402274915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐云路</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-18 13:44:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4517/medium/4517.jpg?1436649750" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


